Athlete
Represents an athlete participating in a sports event.

Controller for managing athlete profiles, including viewing, creating, and updating athlete information.

SecurityConfig
Security configuration class that extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter to customize security settings for the application.

Utility class for generating secure random keys, which can be used in various parts of the security configuration, such as "remember me" functionality.
